metadata.description:
Under the help of two bridesmaids, summer tilt month finally appeared in front of Xiao Che. She was wearing a bright red phoenix crown, and the fine pearl curtain hanging from the crown completely covered her face, making it impossible to see her face and expression at this time. Her long black hair was tied up behind her, and she was dressed in a straight train of bright red robe made of brocade and brocade. Her waist was tied up, stretching out her slender waist. Waist wearing exquisite jade belt, jade belt pendent thin pearl tassel, foot on gold wire, a gorgeous dress in her body even more dazzling.



Summer tilt month under the help of bridesmaids slowly to sedan next to xiao Che, each step is light ethereal grace, as stepping in the clouds. The same is walking, ordinary woman is walking, and in her body, but such as fairy point cloud, this is normal but the posture is beautiful, see Xiao Che is also a feast for the eyes.
